reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent charger and cables
reviews.reviewText: High quality chargers that perform flawlessly and deliver fast charging of a completely dead cell phone. On the average, it take about 10 minutes to bring it back to 100% when the phone is at the 40% level. The price was unbelievably low with extra savings when you buy a pair. I have bought 3 sets for various family members and each person was totally Satisfied with their performance.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works for my Samsung
reviews.reviewText: I'm glad I didn't have to spend a lot of money to replace my old charger, and this pack came with 2 sets! Only need one for now, and glad to have a backup. Charges my s21+ fast. The cord is long, which is a plus. Very good value, Im happy with this purchase!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I was super skeptical ordering because of the pricing I had doubts BUT once I received my package I was blown away. The cords are super long which is a plus and comes with two power boxes to plug into the wall. It is truly fast charging!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good fast charger.
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for my Galaxy A14. I was having a hard time charging it enough before I would call somebody (Busy video calling that special someone). This fast charger was a great price so I decided buying it. Boy was I happy when I got it. It went from about 3% to 50% in a little over a hour. Granted that was with me being busy half the time also playing games on my phone. My old charger would barely charge it to 15% in an hour. Honestly. It beats spending $10 for one at wal-mart.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars 25W exactly as advertised!!!!!
reviews.reviewText: I'm using Samsung A54 5G phone, look at my 2 photos uploaded side-by-side (green is reviewed for this 25W version) vs red (other generic GaN 65W adapter sold here). They both used identical phone on Android 14 with 85% hard limit and super fast charging enabled. I can't get the red version to even show "super fast charging" while the green has no issue charging up in half the time 42 to 85% in just 28minutes!!!! I can't speak for iPhone but Android users running version 14 should have no problem getting same results. This product does not have A54 listed but I confirmed it works exactly at 25W! To the person complaining why they took Samsung logo off well it's because it's illegal. And anyone having issue, make sure you're getting from vendor shijiazhuanghoucha. He got 2 set deal going on under 8 so I have zero expectation and just tested the product an hour ago upon arrival and was blown away that it works exactly as I've been searching, I wasted so much money on garbage that don't work. If you have an A54, just get it!
